    <stitle>STEERING COLUMN ASSEMBLY, TILT/TELESCOPING - OPERATION - TELESCOPE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TELESCOPE</title>
        <para>The column will telescope a total of 2-1/4 inches. To adjust the telescopic position, unlock column by
            pulling the tilt/telescope lever up (toward the steering wheel). Raise or lower the steering to the desired
            position and release the lever to lock the column in position.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
